{"tid":2228474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民再登獅子山 舉「SAVE 12」燈牌","createTime":"2020-10-03T15:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T17:57:10.000Z","uid":94771,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"80cdafecf285646811141df92ea182cd42b56951","tid":2228474,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:05:46.000Z","msg":"市民再登獅子山 舉「SAVE 12」燈牌<br />\n#Video produced by #蘋果日報 #感謝蘋果日報 #SupportAppleDaily #感謝同路人<br />\n<br />\n中秋夜當日，人民無懼警暴，在警方已一早派員守獅子山頭下，堅持一如往年般登頂，以電筒「和你燈」及大喊口號，再創奇蹟。至今日晚上，繼續有市民登上獅子山，在山頭以燈管砌成「SAVE 12」等口號，希望市民毋忘在內地被扣留的12名港人。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果報導: <a href=\"http://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201003/Y7D4LJWE4BDSZEHQQGALVRU7Y4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201003%2FY7D4LJWE4BDSZEHQQGALVRU7Y4&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=cd38e932\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201003%2FY7D4LJWE4BDSZEHQQGALVRU7Y4&h=64734ba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201003/Y7D4LJWE4BDSZEHQQGALVRU7Y4</a><br />\n#save12hkyouths #save12 #釋放十二 #毋忘義士 #釋放義士 #還我公義 #獅子山 #暴政不止 #抗爭不息<br />\n<br />\n有關Twitter :<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BeWaterHKG/status/1312391900645650434?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBeWaterHKG%2Fstatus%2F1312391900645650434%3Fs%3D20&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=0169eff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBeWaterHKG%2Fstatus%2F1312391900645650434%3Fs%3D20&h=c13cc8be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BeWaterHKG/status/1312391900645650434?s=20</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1312396930778046466?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1312396930778046466%3Fs%3D20&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=3428d22e\" dat