":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"推 中共警告：發起聯署呼籲德國制裁或犯法 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2227590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2227590</a>"},{"pid":"49081b3e27d43f67f3b077f0c1dbbe6d4a08282c","tid":2228474,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T16:29:01.000Z","msg":"懷念著你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3f7b0152aa994f313e39f535a7b50df4721ea10b","tid":2228474,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1312281245745737728?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1312281245745737728%3Fs%3D20&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=8021c5a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1312281245745737728%3Fs%3D20&h=2bcf822a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1312281245745737728?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong><ins>入去多謝人</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【港人聯合各民族東京遊行「賀」中共建國 71 年 / #立場報道】<br />\n🎏香港建國聯盟：打正旗號主張港獨<br />\n🎏隊頭拉起以日文寫成的「我哋真係好撚鍾意香港」嘅橫額<br />\n<br />\n今日是 10・1 後首個周末，居於日本的香港人聯同當地西藏、維吾爾、蒙古等民族舉行「中華人民共和國建國 71 周年聯合遊行」，主辦單位宣布約 350 人參加。遊行隊伍中有「香港建國聯盟」的旗幟，該聯盟的 Ken 表示，此為在日本新成立的組織，打正旗號主張港獨。<br />\n<br />\n遊行隊伍首先於日本時間 2 時兵分三路，於新宿、池袋、日比谷各自示威，然後再於當地時間 5 時半，於新宿水之廣場集合遊行。由於遊行路線是鬧市，隊伍吸引不少市民圍觀。<br />\n<br />\n#國際線 #日本 #東京<br />\n#FridaysForFreedom #FreeHongKong #StandWithHongKong #十一 #國殤 #賀佢老母 #天下圍共 #全球滅共<br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=e6ac4b93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1312324877207048193?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1312324877207048193%3Fs%3D20&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=277372a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1312324877207048193%3Fs%3D20&h=2b28c055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1312324877207048193?s=20</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/StandwithHK_JPN/status/1312310183935139840?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStandwithHK_JPN%2Fstatus%2F1312310183935139840%3Fs%3D20&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=4aadcc2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStandwithHK_JPN%2Fstatus%2F1312310183935139840%3Fs%3D20&h=5e193c6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/StandwithHK_JPN/status/1312310183935139840?s=20</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1312244179452403712?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1312244179452403712%3Fs%3D20&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=b61a52ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsuzutaro26%2Fstatus%2F1312244179452403712%3Fs%3D20&h=894f849e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/suzutaro26/status/1312244179452403712?s=20</a>"}}